          <article class="product-review" id="ulei-de-masline-extra-virgin-aur-lichid---250ml">
            <div class="product-review__header">
              <span class="section-tag">Pentru Buget Mic</span>
              <h3>Ulei de Masline Extra Virgin "Aur Lichid" - 250ml</h3>
              <div class="product-review__specs-grid">
